<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cautious-adj">cautious <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kɔːʃəs/    美 /'kɔːʃəs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>十分小心的；谨慎的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Doctors are <strong>cautious about</strong> the new treatment. 
医生们对于这种新疗法很谨慎。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She is very <strong>cautious about</strong> hurting his feelings.
她小心翼翼，唯恐伤了他的感情。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>cautiously /'kɔːʃəsli/ adv   </p></div>